# Git uploads to GitHub

When staging, committing, or pushing to GitHub:
- Do **not** mention Chinese/English change problems, encoding issues, or line-ending (LF/CRLF) warnings in commit messages or in the summary to the user.
- Keep commit messages and upload summaries focused on the actual changes (features, fixes, files).
